11#include "pc/ice_transport.h"
12
13#include "api/sequence_checker.h"
14
15namespace webrtc {
16
17IceTransportWithPointer::~IceTransportWithPointer() {
18 // We depend on the networking thread to call Clear() before dropping
19 // its last reference to this object; if the destructor is called
20 // on the networking thread, it's OK to not have called Clear().
21 if (internal_) {
22 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(creator_thread_);
23 }
24}
25
26cricket::IceTransportInternal* IceTransportWithPointer::internal() {
27 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(creator_thread_);
28 return internal_;
29}
30
31void IceTransportWithPointer::Clear() {
32 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(creator_thread_);
33 internal_ = nullptr;
34}
35
36} // namespace webrtc
